Which of the following commands installs GRUB into the MBR of the second SATA disk?
A)  grub2- install /dev/hdb2
B)  grub2- install /dev/sda2
C)  grub2- config /dev/sda
D)  grub2- install /dev/sdb
D
D. The grub2- install command is used to install GRUB onto a disk. The second SATAdisk would be /dev/sdb, therefore making option D the correct answer.
